

-static is keyword in java
-static means fix (only one copy is created)
-In Java, static means something belongs to the class, not to the object.
-there are three use of static 
  1) static varible
  2) static method
  3) static block

1) static varible
 - only one copy is created.
 - use for auto increment.

* syntax--> static datatype varible;
* Example-->static int a;

